Package: PhytoIn
Type: Package
Title: PhytoIn: Vegetation Inventory Package
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rodrigo Augusto Santinelo Pereira
Maintainer: The package maintainer <raspereira@usp.br>
Description: The PhytoIn package provides a set of functions designed to assist in the analysis 
    of phytosociological data and biomass estimation. The current version includes three main functions. 
    'phytoparam' estimates phytosociological parameters for both plot and point-quarter methods. 
    'AGB' computes the Above Ground Biomass. 'BA.plot' creates a map of the plots used in a vegetation 
    survey and plots the basal area of the sampled trees.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: 
    BIOMASS,
    ggplot2,
    ggforce,
    packcircles
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
